title: I Am...
itunes:title: I Am...
description:
Episode 169 - "I Am..." The sentences or words that follow those two words are the most important words you will ever say. That sentence can either be empowering or disempowering, the choice is yours. In this episode I dive into this topic and tell you how these words can change your life.
